@startuml
skinparam componentStyle uml2
top to bottom direction
skinparam nodesep 70
skinparam ranksep 50

title Component Diagram - Iterazione 4 (Agent Layer)

component "Agent Layer" {

    portin  pAgentIn
    portout pDataOut
    portout pExtOut

    component [Orchestrator Agent] <<component>> as Orch
    component [Classifier Agent]   <<component>> as Classifier
    component [Query Agent]        <<component>> as QueryAg
    component [Web Agent]          <<component>> as WebAg
    component [Generator Agent]    <<component>> as Generator
    component [Revision Agent]     <<component>> as Revision

    interface "IOrchestrator" as IOrch
    interface "IClassifier"   as IClassif
    interface "IQueryAgent"   as IQuery
    interface "IWebAgent"     as IWeb
    interface "IGenerator"    as IGen
    interface "IRevision"     as IRev

    ' ─── Ingresso dal Gateway ─────────────────────────────────
    pAgentIn --> IOrch
    IOrch     -  Orch

    ' ─── Orchestrator → Classifier ────────────────────────────
    Orch     --( IClassif
    IClassif  -  Classifier

    ' ─── Orchestrator → Query Agent ───────────────────────────
    Orch   --( IQuery
    IQuery  -  QueryAg

    ' ─── Orchestrator → Web Agent ─────────────────────────────
    Orch  --( IWeb
    IWeb   -  WebAg

    ' ─── Orchestrator → Generator ─────────────────────────────
    Orch  --( IGen
    IGen   -  Generator

    ' ─── Orchestrator → Revision ──────────────────────────────
    Orch  --( IRev
    IRev   -  Revision

    ' ─── Web Agent → External Services ────────────────────────
    WebAg --> pExtOut

    ' ─── Orchestrator → Data Tier ─────────────────────────────
    Orch --> pDataOut
}

note right of QueryAg
  Genera 6-8 keyword ottimizzate
  per motori di ricerca.
  Decide autonomamente se
  includere info profilo studente.
end note

note right of WebAg
  Tavily API: search_depth="advanced"
  include_domains=[unibg.it,
    coursecatalogue.cineca.it]
  max_results=30 → top 5 per score.
  Estrae link da PDF (PyMuPDF).
end note

note bottom of Orch
  LangGraph StateGraph:
  classify → query → web_search → generate → revise
end note

@enduml
